    "They also disagree that writing tools could help them evaluate writing outputs, condensed text to its most important and relevant ideas, identify writing weaknesses to promote self-assessment and learning, experiment with different styles and ideas, outline topic and brainstorm ideas, improve their paraphrasing and grammar skills, and improve the clarity of their ideas.",
